<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="W" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Wren" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Wren,</orth> the bird Troglodytes parvulus: <bibl n="shak. mnd 3.1.131" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. III, 1, 131</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 5.106" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. V, 106</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.2.42" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B III, 2, 42</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.3.71" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 3, 71</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 4.2.9" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. IV, 2, 9</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 4.6.114" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. IV, 6, 114</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 4.2.305" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. IV, 2, 305</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. per 4.3.22" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. IV, 3, 22</bibl>. Sir Toby calls Maria <emph>the youngest w. of mine</emph> (M. Edd. <emph>of nine</emph>), <bibl n="shak. tn 3.2.70" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. III, 2, 70</bibl>, on account of her short stature.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>